ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations and Employment Board Act
SubjectOrder (1) Repealing Order in Council P.C. 2018-1200 of September 25, 2018; and (2) Designating the Minister of Democratic Institutions to be the Minister referred to in the Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2018-1200 of September 25, 2018; and (2) designating the MINISTER OF DEMOCRATIC INSTITUTIONS, who is not a member of the Treasury Board, to be the MINISTER referred to in the FEDERAL PUBLIC SECTOR LABOUR RELATIONS AND EMPLOYMENT BOARD ACT.
